column4: Can anyone help me with my resolution, there are 4 in my xorg.conf but in gnome only 1
Got anywhere you can post your xorg.conf?
Hold on I'm looking at it.  What resolution are you running currently, and what resolution can you choose in gnome?
I don't see any problems so far.  What type of graphics are you using?
I'm thinking we need to have a look at the xorg log
If there's some error on the server startup it'd be in there
There aren't any errors near the bottom of the log?
ill be back in half an hour or something, could you say everything in query please? thanks.
